<div class='otherEdition' id='edition_10381144'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/10381144-the-joy-luck-club"><img alt="The Joy Luck Club" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1624664703i/10381144._UY200_.jpg" />
