<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I feel that this book is great for a book club. Everyone can chime in with something new because it&apos;s filled with symbolism, visualizations, and conne<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I feel that this book is great for a book club. Everyone can chime in with something new because it's filled with symbolism, visualizations, and connections to the reader. Basic human fears, hopes, joys, and place in society can help with that connection. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
